<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.8.3">
<l>kumarima ṇañceytu koṇṭu kōlañcey tillat tirutti</l>
<l>tamarum piṟarumaṟi yattā mōtaraṟ keṉṟu cāṟṟi</l>
<l>yamarar patiyuṭait tēvi yaracā ṇiyaivaḻi paṭṭu</l>
<l>tumila meḻappaṟai koṭṭit tōraṇam nāṭṭiṭuṅ kolō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>They will perform a marriage [for the] girl,</l>
<l rend="indent">adorning [her] with [the appropriate] garments,</l>
<l>seating her in the hall, [and] announcing that [she is]</l>
<l rend="indent">for Dāmodara so that relations and others know,</l>
<l>the wife of the immortals’ lord</l>
<l rend="indent">adhering to the [ritual of the] pipal branch,</l>
<l>beating drums so that the din rises,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] set up a festooned archway, won’t they?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
